            <title>[LU-19098] don&apos;t print progname twice in lhsmtool log messages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19098</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since Lustre 2.11, log message from &lt;tt&gt;llapi_error()&lt;/tt&gt; prefixes the message to print with the current program do the same. There is no more a need for lhsmtool_posix log fonctions (CT_xxxx) to also do the same.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
